Class LinkedBinarySearchTree<T>

java.lang.Object

Custom_CollectionsED.trees.binary.binaryLinkedTree.LinkedBinarySearchTree<T>
Type Parameters:
T -
All Implemented Interfaces:
BinarySearchTreeADT<T>, BinaryTreeADT<T>, trees.binary.interfaces.BinaryTreeADT<T>
public class LinkedBinarySearchTree<T> extends LinkedBinaryTree<T> implements BinarySearchTreeADT<T>
This class is a representation of a binary search tree, implemented through the use of a linked list. Each node of the list contains references to its children. It implements the BinarySearchTreeADT interface, and extends the LinkedBinaryTree abstract class
